<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3767614>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Marbefia carthyi (Hamond, 1968), comb. n. (♀): A urosome, ventral [excluding P5-bearing somite] B anal somite and caudal rami, dorsal C rostrum, dorsal D antennule, ventral E labrum, anterior F paragnaths, anterior G genital area with P6 [copulatory pore arrowed]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3767614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3767616>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Marbefia carthyi (Hamond, 1968), comb. n. (♀): A antenna B mandibular palp C maxillule, anterior D maxilla, posterior E maxilliped, posterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3767616/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3767622>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Marbefia carthyi (Hamond, 1968), comb. n.: A antennule ♁, ventral [armature on segments 3, 4 and 8 omitted] B antennulary segments 3 (right) and 4 (left) ♁ C antennulary segment 8 ♁ D P5 and P6 ♁, anterior E P5 ♀, anterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3767622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3767618>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Marbefia carthyi (Hamond, 1968), comb. n.: A P1 ♀, anterior B P4 ♀, anterior [inner seta on enp-1 arrowed] C P4 endopod ♁, anterior [spinular rows on enp-1 arrowed] D distal part of P4 endopod ♀, posterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3767618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3767620>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Marbefia carthyi (Hamond, 1968), comb. n.: A P2 ♀, anterior, B P2 endopod ♀, outer lateral C P3 ♀, anterior [inner seta on enp-1 arrowed] D P3 endopod ♁ [spinules on enp-1 and apophysis on enp-2 arrowed]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3767620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

